{
  "stem": "10768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, when you-- when you go there, when you come to Lublin, you come there and ask about my sister because somebody told me that she survived somewhere in Plaszow, in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, Krakow was still-- no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that she survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Krakow was still German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The trains were really not running again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as a soldier, a little bit hitchhiking, I was not aware that I could have been raped, that I could have been killed either because of the depression of knowing already what happened-- my brother was not with me.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was from [INAUDIBLE] taken to the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was from [INAUDIBLE] taken to a working establishment somewhere also in Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, he was mobilized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had no idea where my brother was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was really alone there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was depressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that time-- or maybe one is young and very naive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I did not really realize in what-- how I endangered myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyhow, I came by train to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in Lublin was the day when Majdanek was nearby Lublin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at that time, the Jewish survivors who survived from the area, surrounding area, were all in, in one huge buildings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't go anywhere else to look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was a group of people who already managed to survive to do a little bit of black marketeering and exchanging a piece of bread for a piece of clothing or whatever.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at that time in Majdanek, the one who was-- the German or the Polish who was the head in Majdanek of the camp was at that time shot or hung by-- I don't know if by survivors or by the Russian or the Polish who came there.",
      "word_count": 48
    }
  ],
